          "en": "He said: Abul Qasim Ja'far ibn Muhammad informed me, from his father, from Sa'd ibn Abdillah, from Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn Isa, from Muhammad ibn Sinan, from Hammad ibn Uthman, from Rabi' ibn Abdillah and al-Fudhayl ibn Yasar, from Abu Abdillah Ja'far ibn Muhammad (peace be upon them both) who said:",
